      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "5f42bdb466d72372",
      "text": "These observations point far beyond the politics of the day and are more relevant than ever in the current crisis of the political system. For this reason alone, repeated reading is recommended. (Tom Levold, Köln)"
    }
